  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1305590/extras/a9cd7b74346836298e6c005cb9de5bf2.avif?t=1752935900\" width=616 height=162 /></span><br><br>Wibbly Witches is a fast and frantic couch competition for 2-4 players. Use spells creatively to outsmart your friends as you fight across unique arenas that become more dangerous as the match progresses.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1305590/extras/f9c6657eb36f602b31a5b3daf772a3b9.avif?t=1752935900\" width=616 height=162 /></span><br>Battle alongside an assortment of creatures and hazards that will appear as the competition gets heated. Hide from giant crabs and spiders, dodge spinning buzz saws and struggle against the elements atop swaying towers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1305590/extras/f1edaa114ddbe23aedaedb0d99b040d4.avif?t=1752935900\" width=616 height=162 /></span><br>Wield powerful and unusual spells against your friends! Ranging from dramatic explosives and screaming comets to a shotgun blasts of dust. While some spells seem useless at first, their full potential can be unlocked by a truly creative caster. Battles are won more through careful mind games than force.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1305590/extras/c893a3bb79f8d7db46f3e0fa39d5ebff.avif?t=1752935900\" width=616 height=162 /></span><br><br>A wyrd and wobbly world awaits you!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1305590/extras/a9cd7b74346836298e6c005cb9de5bf2.avif?t=1752935900\" width=616 height=162 /></span><br><br>Wibbly Witches is a fast and frantic couch competition for 2-4 players. Use spells creatively to outsmart your friends as you fight across unique arenas that become more dangerous as the match progresses.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1305590/extras/f9c6657eb36f602b31a5b3daf772a3b9.avif?t=1752935900\" width=616 height=162 /></span><br>Battle alongside an assortment of creatures and hazards that will appear as the competition gets heated. Hide from giant crabs and spiders, dodge spinning buzz saws and struggle against the elements atop swaying towers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1305590/extras/f1edaa114ddbe23aedaedb0d99b040d4.avif?t=1752935900\" width=616 height=162 /></span><br>Wield powerful and unusual spells against your friends! Ranging from dramatic explosives and screaming comets to a shotgun blasts of dust. While some spells seem useless at first, their full potential can be unlocked by a truly creative caster. Battles are won more through careful mind games than force.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1305590/extras/c893a3bb79f8d7db46f3e0fa39d5ebff.avif?t=1752935900\" width=616 height=162 /></span><br><br>A wyrd and wobbly world awaits you!",
